    • enrollStudent

      public boolean enrollStudent(Student student)
      Enrolls a student in the course section. Enrollment is unsuccessful if the student is already enrolled in the section or if the section has reached its maximum capacity.
      Parameters:
      student - the student to enroll
      Returns:
      true if enrollment is successful, false if:
      • The student is already enrolled in the section
      • The section has reached its maximum capacity

    • dropStudent

      public boolean dropStudent(Student student)
      Drops a student from the course section. Dropping is unsuccessful if the student is not enrolled in the section.
      Parameters:
      student - the student to drop
      Returns:
      true if dropping is successful, false if:
      • The student is not enrolled in the section

    • assignInstructor

      public void assignInstructor(Instructor instructor)
      Assigns an instructor to the course section. If the section already has an instructor, the current instructor is removed before assigning the new instructor.
      Parameters:
      instructor - the instructor to assign
